full_threads.body:
Hi Nic,

Thanks for confirming the details. Here's how we'll line this up:
  1. Wildcard Redirect: @Joel Maligalig from our team will set up the wildcard redirect on the hosting side so all URLs (including sub-pages and PDFs) point to the new landing page. We'll ensure this is live by Thursday morning.
  2. Testing: Once the redirect is in place, we'll test the main URL and all known sub-URLs you've shared to confirm everything is working correctly.
  3. Billing: @Victoria Victoria will set up the hosting subscription and add the $45/month charge to the invoices, referencing "JT Insurance Redirect". The invoice will be sent to Aviso Integral.
  4. DNS: Joel will also confirm any DNS record changes required to make sure everything routes correctly. We'll coordinate with your team to complete those Thursday morning.
We'll confirm back once the redirect is live and tested.

Thanks,
Andy

****
